PrecisAppointment of THOMAS D. MULLINS, of Dollard-des-Ormeaux, Quebec, as a member of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective April 1, 1999; and order that THOMAS D. MULLINS be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
